Quickstrike:










Quickstrike was getting annoyed. His foreclaw hurt and his head was still 
light. Without saying a word to Transulas, he slowly crawls off. He needed 
repairs, badly. This Tarantsulus clone wasn't doing anything for him right 
now. That mad him mad. He wondered how the Predacons base was doing---if it 
had fired, and if Hell Beast's troops were shelterless by now. The only way 
he could find out was go there himself.

He gave Trantsulas a last look, in his head, picturing the Predacons base. 
He wasn't feeling good at all. Maybe he could actually sneek inside the 
base. The computer would never announce his presence, because it saw him as 
master and programer.
